{
  "action": "pipeline",
  "pipeline_id": "account-expansion-workflow",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "name": "Account Expansion — Upsell Workflow",
  "description": "既存顧客チェックインコールから拡張トリガーを識別し、アップセル評価・拡張提案書・後継ミッションブリーフ・ゲートアーティファクトを生成する account_expansion Track 用パイプライン。",
  "context": {
    "mission_id": "",
    "project_name": "",
    "language": "ja",
    "account_name": "",
    "account_person_slug": "",
    "account_org": "",
    "existing_contract_ref": "",
    "existing_mission_ref": ""
  },
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "log_start",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": {
        "message": "🔄 [EXPANSION] Starting account expansion workflow (mission: {{mission_id}}, account: {{account_org}})"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "read_checkin",
      "type": "capture",
      "op": "system:read_file",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/checkin-call-transcript.txt",
        "export_as": "checkin_text"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_checkin",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": {
        "message": "📄 Check-in call transcript loaded ({{mission_evidence_dir}}/checkin-call-transcript.txt)"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "analyze_expansion_trigger",
      "type": "transform",
      "op": "reasoning:analyze",
      "params": {
        "instruction": "以下の既存顧客チェックインコール記録を分析し、アップセル・拡張機会を特定してください。\n\n## 分析項目\n1. 既存契約スコープ（参照: {{existing_contract_ref}}）\n2. チェックインで浮上した新たな課題・ニーズ（具体的に）\n3. 既存スコープとの差分（なぜ既存契約で対応できないか）\n4. 拡張機会の規模感（概算）\n5. 顧客のレディネス（即決/要検討/長期）\n6. 競合リスク（他社に取られる可能性）\n\n## 出力形式（Markdown）\n### 拡張トリガー\n### 新たな課題・ニーズ\n### 既存スコープとの差分\n### 拡張機会の評価\n| 項目 | 評価 |\n|---|---|\n| 規模感 | |\n| 顧客レディネス | |\n| 競合リスク | |\n### 推奨アクション",
        "context": ["{{mission_id}}", "{{account_org}}", "{{account_name}}", "{{existing_contract_ref}}"],
        "export_as": "expansion_trigger"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "write_trigger",
      "type": "apply",
      "op": "code:write_artifact",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/expansion-trigger-analysis.md",
        "content": "{{expansion_trigger}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_trigger",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": {
        "message": "🎯 [EXPANSION] Expansion trigger analyzed → {{mission_evidence_dir}}/expansion-trigger-analysis.md"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "generate_expansion_proposal",
      "type": "transform",
      "op": "reasoning:analyze",
      "params": {
        "instruction": "以下の情報を統合して、既存顧客向けアップセル提案書をMarkdown形式で作成してください。\n\n重要: 前置き文・説明文・挨拶文は不要です。提案書の本文のみを出力してください。最初の行は必ず '# ' で始まるMarkdown見出しにしてください。\n\n# コンテキスト\n- 顧客: {{account_org}} / {{account_name}}\n- 既存契約: {{existing_contract_ref}}\n- プロジェクト名: {{project_name}}\n- 拡張トリガー分析: {{expansion_trigger}}\n\n# 提案書の構成（以下の見出し構造を必ず守ること）\n## はじめに（既存関係の文脈）\n## 今回ご提案する拡張内容\n### 課題の整理\n### ソリューション概要\n### 既存システム（{{existing_contract_ref}}）との連携方法\n## 技術実現性\n### アーキテクチャ概要\n### 必要な前提条件・サンプルデータ\n## ROI・期待効果\n| 効果項目 | 試算 | 根拠 |\n|---|---|---|\n## 導入フェーズ\n| フェーズ | 期間 | 成果物 |\n|---|---|---|\n## 投資概算\n## 次のステップ（顧客への依頼事項）",
        "context": ["{{mission_id}}", "{{account_org}}", "{{existing_contract_ref}}"],
        "export_as": "expansion_proposal_content"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "write_expansion_brief",
      "type": "apply",
      "op": "code:write_artifact",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/expansion-brief.md",
        "content": "{{expansion_proposal_content}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_expansion_brief",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": {
        "message": "📋 [EXPANSION] Expansion brief written → {{mission_evidence_dir}}/expansion-brief.md"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "record_upsell_gate",
      "type": "apply",
      "op": "system:write_file",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/upsell-qualification-gate.json",
        "content": {
          "gate": "UPSELL_QUALIFICATION_GATE",
          "track": "account_expansion",
          "status": "pending_operator_confirmation",
          "account": "{{account_org}} / {{account_name}}",
          "existing_contract": "{{existing_contract_ref}}",
          "artifacts": [
            "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/expansion-trigger-analysis.md",
            "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/expansion-brief.md"
          ],
          "instructions": "拡張提案の内容を確認し、顧客に提示可能と判断したら status を 'passed' に更新してください。承認後、後継ミッション（product_discovery or delivery Track）を mission_controller create で起票してください。",
          "created_at": "{{$now}}"
        },
        "format": "json"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "write_successor_brief",
      "type": "apply",
      "op": "system:write_file",
      "params": {
        "path": "{{mission_evidence_dir}}/successor-mission-brief.json",
        "content": {
          "status": "pending",
          "trigger_mission": "{{mission_id}}",
          "suggested_track": "product_discovery",
          "suggested_title": "{{project_name}}: 拡張フェーズ — 詳細ヒアリング・要件定義",
          "suggested_pipeline": "pipelines/customer-discovery-workflow.json",
          "account": "{{account_org}} / {{account_name}}",
          "existing_contract": "{{existing_contract_ref}}",
          "instructions": "このブリーフを参照して mission_controller create を実行し、後継ミッションを起票してください。顧客のサインオフ確認後に実施を推奨。",
          "created_at": "{{$now}}"
        },
        "format": "json"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "log_done",
      "op": "system:log",
      "params": {
        "message": "🏁 [EXPANSION] Pipeline complete. Artifacts in {{mission_evidence_dir}}. Next: review expansion brief → present to account → confirm upsell gate → create successor mission."
      }
    }
  ]
}
